OL,6,FA man has been jailed after stealing
OL,7,Fchocolate from a shop he was banned
OL,8,Ffrom entering.
OL,10,FMartin Toon, aged 32, was issued with
OL,11,Fa Criminal Behaviour Order by a
OL,12,Fmagistrate in November last year,
OL,13,Fbanning him from all Co-Op stores
OL,15,FOn Monday 5 February, he was caught on
OL,16,FCCTV as he walked into the Co-Op
OL,17,Fbranch in , and helped himself to
OL,18,Fchocolate bars worth around #30.
OL,20,FWhen challenged, he then threatened to
OL,21,Fassault a staff member.
