OL,6,FToon, Welbeck Street, Sutton, was
OL,7,Farrested on Wednesday and pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty the following day to theft,
OL,9,Fbreaching a Criminal Behaviour Order,
OL,10,Fand an offence under the Public Order
OL,11,FAct.
OL,13,FAppearing at Nottingham Magistrates
OL,14,FCourt, he was jailed for eight weeks.
OL,16,FPC Charles Richmond, of
OL,17,FNottinghamshire Police, said:
